&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;정월대보름, 소원성취 달집 태우기&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span&gt;오늘은 정월대보름&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span&gt;오곡밥과 아홉가지 나물을 먹고&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span&gt;달집태우기 행사장에 가 보았습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile29.uf.tistory.com/image/211DA44F56CB0B733287BD&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile8.uf.tistory.com/image/254F463656CB0B74197325&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile21.uf.tistory.com/image/2631C03756CB0B7501F35D&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/237AFE3556CB0B760B9ACD&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/image/211F833C56CB0B7733ADE6&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/213BFD3356CB0B780D0AC8&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/2721BA3356CB0B79170FAB&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile3.uf.tistory.com/image/262DFB3856CB0B7A055BC0&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile2.uf.tistory.com/image/2638693956CB0B7B317729&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span&gt;활활 타오르는 달집을 보